  "body": "Reported by @etan-status from Nimbus team.\r\n\r\nOur CL pivot updater fails to address the edge case when FinalizedBlockHash in FCU is Keccak.Zero.\r\nThis situation proves beneficial during devnet transitions and holds even more significance for lightclients.\r\nNethermind waits for the finalized block hash to start synchronization. One potential solution could be implementing an exception for Keccak.Zero.\r\n\r\n\r\nReproduction - Nethermind instruction here: https://nimbus.guide/el-light-client.html",
